metadata.description: NEAR Event Planner helps you to  organize events by allow registrants to deposit NEAR into a smart contract to pay for the event (e.g. boat rental). If the minimum threshold or minimal participant threshold is met, the event beneficiary can claim the amount and pay for the event. If the threshold is not met, the event is cancelled and the fund is returned to each registrant. Host your event today!
metadata.name: Event Planner
